      <hedline>
        <hl1>Debating Global Warming</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>David Del Sesto letter on December 3 article supports Bush administration's call to further investigate global warming</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>If the administration wants to investigate climate change and global warming further, fine (''Global Warming''). It's a good idea, as is a swift call to action for at least initiating a solution to this worldwide problem.</p>
        <p>DAVID DEL SESTO  Smithfield, R.I.</p>
      </block>
